{"tid":2246231,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[民調] 原來香港人多數支持拜登","createTime":"2020-10-17T01:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T05:57:40.000Z","uid":323443,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"981d854b44c33360d2fa55164bd34c8ca8fd43b0","tid":2246231,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:26:46.000Z","msg":"跨國民調機構「輿觀」（YouGov）15日公布向亞太8國民調的結果，有42%的台灣民眾支持川普連任，為亞太區最高數據，也是唯一支持度超過拜登的國家。<br />\n<br />\n台灣受訪者認為川普連任會對台灣利大於弊（45%對33%），但認為如果是拜登執政則弊大於利（28%對26%）。但問題對「個人」而非國家的影響，只有27%受訪者認為帶來好處，有29%覺得更差。<br />\n <br />\n新加坡、印尼、馬來西亞、澳洲的民調結果都顯示，拜登的支持率狂輾川普2倍以上，只有香港以拜登42%、川普36%的差距為最小。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/EzQlqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FEzQlqg&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24haoxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=8869a574\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/EzQlqg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0eab57043edd2f3109cbcd7efcec1dce7df831","tid":2246231,"uid":294518,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />臺灣人清醒"},{"pid":"5b5365a423992c3f964ad9321d239bea86e68261","tid":2246231,"uid":155095,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T01:35:19.000Z","msg":"不嬲連登唔等於香港多數人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2016/11/257fa4b687a6406ab4235826de290b25.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2016%2F11%2F257fa4b687a6406ab4235826de290b25.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=d52c64da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets